<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="700">
    <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#ffffff" valign="top" colspan="18">
            <!-- CONTENT: Public-facing registration information, steps, payment and refund policy -->
            <div class="content">
                <p class="style13">Registration</p>

                <p><span class="highlight">Don't wait long to register, spots are filling up fast!</span></p>

                <p>We have a registration process that we follow to ensure a spot for your child:</p>

                <h2>Registration Steps:</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Choose your preferred week(s)</strong> (you may want to choose a 1st and 2nd choice)</li>
                    <li><strong>Email me</strong> (BEFORE sending in your registration and check) so I can pencil you in for that week.</li>
                    <li><strong>Fill out the online registration form</strong> here: <a href="/register" class="highlight">ONLINE REGISTRATION</a></li>
                </ol>

                <h2>Payment ($125)</h2>
                <p>Payment ($125) can be made through one of the following methods:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Venmo:</strong> @Csaf16 (please don't send as a business payment, I am charged a fee)</li>
                    <li><strong>Check:</strong> Send your check payable to Jennifer Safsten to the following address:
                        <div style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 8px; font-style: italic;">
                            Jennifer Safsten<br>
                            13485 Four Seasons Ct<br>
                            Mt. Airy, MD 21771
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <p>Once your payment is received, this will guarantee your spot for that week.</p>

                <p><strong>Note:</strong> Payments MUST be received within 1 week of reserving a spot (unless other arrangements are made). If not received within one week, the spot will become available to other participants.</p>

                <h2>Refund Policy</h2>
                <p>There are NO refunds, deductions, or credits granted for any missed class or camp. However, we offer a generous make-up policy. Make-up classes are available for any class missed due to illness.</p>

                <p style="text-align: center;">
                    <a href="/register" class="btn-register">Fill Out Registration Form</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </td>
    </tr>
